+# Project Structure Guide
+
+## Core Directories
+- `src/app`: Next.js App Router pages en layouts
+- `src/components`: UI componenten (atoms, molecules, organisms)
+- `src/lib`: Gedeelde utilities en helpers
+- `src/hooks`: Custom React hooks
+- `src/types`: TypeScript type definities
+- `src/styles`: Global styles en Tailwind configuratie
+- `src/server`: Server-side code (tRPC, API routes)
+- `src/utils`: Helper functies en utilities
+
+## Key Files
+- `src/app/layout.tsx`: Root layout met providers
+- `src/app/page.tsx`: Homepage met scan formulier
+- `src/app/api/trpc/[trpc]/route.ts`: tRPC API endpoints
+- `src/server/api/trpc.ts`: tRPC server setup
+- `src/server/db/index.ts`: Database configuratie
+- `src/components/ui`: shadcn/ui componenten
+- `src/lib/firebase.ts`: Firebase configuratie
+- `src/types/index.ts`: Globale type definities
+
+## Component Organization
+Components volgen Atomic Design principes:
+- `atoms/`: Basis UI elementen (Button, Input)
+- `molecules/`: Combinaties van atoms (ScanForm)
+- `organisms/`: Complexe secties (ScanResults)
+- `templates/`: Pagina layouts
+- `pages/`: Concrete implementaties


